{
  "$schema": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/DjobaDELATV/seygo_data/main/schema/v1/card.json",
  "id": "a4aaa2a4-1bd0-4802-bc6e-94451ad029d1",
  "text": {
    "en": {
      "name": "Elemental HERO Wild Wingman",
      "effect": "\"Elemental HERO Wildheart\" + \"Elemental HERO Avian\"\nMust be Fusion Summoned. You can discard 1 card, then target 1 Spell/Trap on the field; destroy that target."
    },
    "fr": {
      "name": "Homme-Oiseau Sauvage, H\u00c9ROS \u00c9l\u00e9mentaire",
      "effect": "\"C\u0153ur Farouche, H\u00c9ROS \u00c9l\u00e9mentaire\" + \"Avian, H\u00c9ROS \u00c9l\u00e9mentaire\"\nUniquement Invocable par Fusion. Vous pouvez d\u00e9fausser 1 carte, puis ciblez 1 Magie/Pi\u00e8ge sur le Terrain ; d\u00e9truisez la cible."
    },
    "de": {
      "name": "Elementar-HELD Wild Wingman",
      "effect": "\u201eElementar-HELD Wildheart\u201c + \u201eElementar-HELD Avian\u201c\nMuss als Fusionsbeschw\u00f6rung beschworen werden und kann nicht auf andere Art als Spezialbeschw\u00f6rung beschworen werden. Du kannst 1 Karte abwerfen, um 1 Zauber-/Fallenkarte auf dem Spielfeld zu w\u00e4hlen; zerst\u00f6re das gew\u00e4hlte Ziel."
    },
    "it": {
      "name": "Uomo Alato Selvaggio EROE Elementale",
      "effect": "\"Wildheart EROE Elementale\" + \"Avian EROE Elementale\"\nDeve essere Evocato tramite Fusione e non pu\u00f2 essere Evocato Specialmente in altri modi. Puoi scartare 1 carta per scegliere come bersaglio 1 Carta Magia/Trappola sul Terreno; distruggi quel bersaglio."
    },
    "pt": {
      "name": "Homem-Alado Selvagem, o HER\u00d3I do Elemento",
      "effect": "\"Cora\u00e7\u00e3o Selvagem, o HER\u00d3I do Elemento\" + \"Avi\u00e1rio, o HER\u00d3I do Elemento\"\nDeve ser Invocado por Invoca\u00e7\u00e3o-Fus\u00e3o. Voc\u00ea pode descartar 1 card e, depois, escolha 1 Magia/Armadilha no campo; destrua o alvo."
    },
    "es": {
      "name": "H\u00c9ROE Elemental Wild Wingman",
      "effect": "\"H\u00c9ROE Elemental Wildheart\" + \"H\u00c9ROE Elemental Avian\"\nEste monstruo no puede ser Invocado mediante una Invocaci\u00f3n Especial excepto mediante una Invocaci\u00f3n de Fusi\u00f3n. Descarta 1 carta de tu mano para destruir 1 Carta M\u00e1gica o de Trampa en el Campo."
    },
    "ja": {
      "name": "\uff25\u30fb\uff28\uff25\uff32\uff2f \u30ef\u30a4\u30eb\u30c9\u30fb\u30a6\u30a3\u30f3\u30b0\u30de\u30f3",
      "effect": "\u300c\uff25\u30fb\uff28\uff25\uff32\uff2f \u30ef\u30a4\u30eb\u30c9\u30de\u30f3\u300d\uff0b\u300c\uff25\u30fb\uff28\uff25\uff32\uff2f \u30d5\u30a7\u30b6\u30fc\u30de\u30f3\u300d\n\u3053\u306e\u30e2\u30f3\u30b9\u30bf\u30fc\u306f\u878d\u5408\u53ec\u559a\u3067\u3057\u304b\u7279\u6b8a\u53ec\u559a\u3067\u304d\u306a\u3044\u3002\u624b\u672d\u3092\uff11\u679a\u6368\u3066\u308b\u4e8b\u3067\u3001\u30d5\u30a3\u30fc\u30eb\u30c9\u4e0a\u306e\u9b54\u6cd5\u30fb\u7f60\u30ab\u30fc\u30c9\uff11\u679a\u3092\u7834\u58ca\u3059\u308b\u3002"
    },
    "ko": {
      "name": "\uc5d8\ub9ac\uba58\ud2c0 \ud788\uc5b4\ub85c \uc640\uc77c\ub4dc \uc719\ub9e8",
      "effect": "\"\uc5d8\ub9ac\uba58\ud2c0 \ud788\uc5b4\ub85c \uc640\uc77c\ub4dc\ub9e8\" + \"\uc5d8\ub9ac\uba58\ud2c0 \ud788\uc5b4\ub85c \ud398\ub354\ub9e8\"\n\uc774 \ubaac\uc2a4\ud130\ub294 \uc735\ud569 \uc18c\ud658\uc73c\ub85c\ubc16\uc5d0 \ud2b9\uc218 \uc18c\ud658\ud560 \uc218 \uc5c6\ub2e4. \ud328\ub97c 1\uc7a5 \ubc84\ub9ac\ub294 \uac83\uc73c\ub85c, \ud544\ub4dc \uc704\uc758 \ub9c8\ubc95 / \ud568\uc815 \uce74\ub4dc 1\uc7a5\uc744 \ud30c\uad34\ud55c\ub2e4."
    }
